        <title>建议大家尽早开始搭建个人知识库</title>
        <link>https://ai.programnotes.cn/p/%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%BD%E6%97%A9%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93/</link>
